// This enum must align with the enum defined in cc/backend.h.
export enum CppDType {
  float32 = 0,
  int32 = 1,
  bool = 2,
  string = 3,
  complex64 = 4
}

// Must match enum in cc/fusable_activations.h.
export enum FusableActivation {
  linear = 0,
  relu = 1,
  relu6 = 2,
  prelu = 3
}
